{
  "stem": "13219.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They already had the second front open.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were fighting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were coming down from, from the, the-- from--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Normandy, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By the Poles, against Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was a stabbing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think they killed-- but I ran away with my-- a few of us ran away.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next few days--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the next few weeks we decided that we're going to have to go farther south.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went into that-- to the place where there was supposed to be an office.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we gave our names that we want to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And after a week or so, they gave us-- they gave us a lecture that you're going to be, as Greek refugees, going back to Greece from the concentration camp in Poland.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave us each false names, which I don't even remember the name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the only thing I remember is when they told us if you see a Russian soldier in the train, just say [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And don't speak any Russian, Russian or Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Greek.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at that time, it was in the night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And about 3:00 in the morning, we went-- we came with a train to Pilzno, Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, when we went off the train and then we saw the first-- The train-- when we came from Poland, they didn't ask us anything.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean the Polish-- the Russian soldiers were on the train, but they didn't bother us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we came to Pilzno, there was already the American zone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we saw the first black people as Americans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we stayed in, in, in Pilzno about two weeks in makeshift buildings, which they gave us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of 1944.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, 1944. '44 I left.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, yeah, '44.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
